{
  "texts": [
    "Future research could investigate these relationships more explicitly by collecting individual information on the organizational resources of interest.",
    "Recent management research started using methods such as qualitative comparative analysis (e.g., Leppänen et al., 2023), which can identify specific configurations of variables that lead to certain outcomes.",
    "We urge further research to explore such methods in this context.",
    "This study focused explicitly on HR-related AI implementation ability.",
    "Human resources are one and arguably the most critical factor in implementing AI (Jöhnk et al., 2020; Mikalef & Gupta, 2021)."
  ]
}